Subject: [PATCH v3] kernel/module.c: Only return -EEXIST for modules that have finished loading
Date:   Wed, 29 May 2019 07:26:25 -0400
Message-Id: <20190529112625.28699-1-prarit@redhat.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
